dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Henry Cooper. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Cynthia Ward.
Nice to meet you, Cynthia. To assist you better, could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is five zero three four two.
Thank you, Cynthia. Additionally, could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle for verification purposes?
Of course, I drive a blue Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss regarding your current policy, Cynthia?
I wanted to inquire about adding roadside assistance to my coverage.
Certainly, Cynthia. I can assist you with that. Thank you for your time today. Is there anything else I can help you with?
No, that's all. Thank you, Henry.
You're welcome, Cynthia. Have a wonderful day! Goodbye.
